title: 820-00923 20v 0.78A braindead
message:
Hello!, got 820-00923 board with no signs of liquid damage. Turns on: 
[LIST]
[*]Trackpad active 
[*]no usb activity 
[*]no external image
[*]no caps lock
[*]cpu gets hot and fans stats to spin after a few minutes
[/LIST]
CPU core voltage goes from 1V to 0.7. Tried good known bios that i found posted in this forum. Any measures i missed that would be important to check?
